## Basic commands

### minikube
minikube start

minikube dashboard

minikube ssh

### Kubectl
kubectl cluster-info

kubectl create -f <file.yaml>

kubectl get pods

kubectl describe pod <pod name>

kubectl get nodes

kubectl describe <node>

kubectl describe po <pod>

kubectl logs <pod>

kubectl exec <pod> -it -- sh



docker commit daad73b4daf2 danieleporta/my-private-repo:version1


